      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but you may notice some minor fluid seeps and suspension noise over bumps. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading, while the interior shows typical wear on the driver's seat and carpets. It is a solid choice for someone needing dependable transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
