    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended primarily for parts or as a major restoration project. The engine currently struggles to stay running, and there is significant rust along the rocker panels and wheel wells. The interior shows heavy wear, including several tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. While it does roll and steer, it will likely need to be towed to its next destination. This is an honest project car for someone with the time and tools to address its many needs.",
