    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example retains its visceral performance thanks to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring the valvetrain and structural integrity meet enthusiast standards. Suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings, offering the telepathic turn-in these cars are known for. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car ready for the apex.",
